ZH: 我们应该向前看，而不是抱怨过去。
EN: We should look forward and not dwell on the past.

ZH: 在困难时期，要勇敢向前迈进。
EN: In times of difficulty, we must bravely move forward.

ZH: 不要害怕失败，只要向前努力就能成功。
EN: Don't be afraid of failure, as long as you strive forward you can succeed.

ZH: 他们迈开腿向前跑去。
EN: They ran forward with long strides.

ZH: 向前走几步，看看能否找到出路。
EN: Take a few steps forward and see if you can find a way out.

ZH: 当遇到问题时，我们唯有向前寻找解决方法。
EN: When faced with a problem, we must move forward in search of a solution.

ZH: 勇敢向前迈进，终有一天你会实现梦想。
EN: Brave forward and one day you will achieve your dreams.

ZH: 知道向前走是正确的选择，但我心有放不下。
EN: Knowing that moving forward is the right choice, but I can't let go of my heart.

ZH: 他一直向前走，在困难面前从不退缩。
EN: He has always moved forward and never backed down in the face of difficulties.

ZH: 不管有多困难，我们都要向前看。
EN: No matter how difficult it is, we must look forward.

ZH: 冒险是向前进步的第一步。
EN: Taking risks is the first step to moving forward.

ZH: 他一直在向前推进，从不放弃。
EN: He has been pushing forward and never giving up.

ZH: 向前看，不要因为过去而困扰。
EN: Look forward and don't be troubled by the past.

ZH: 向前走，不要回头看。
EN: Move forward and don't look back.

ZH: 我们要向前看，才能看到前方的希望。
EN: We must look forward to see the hope ahead.

ZH: 他一直向前冲，终于获得了他想要的结果。
EN: He kept pushing forward and finally achieved the results he wanted.

ZH: 没有一个强大的意志，是无法向前迈进的。
EN: Without a strong will, one cannot move forward.

ZH: 不要被困境困住，要向前走才能获得解脱。
EN: Don't be trapped in difficulties, only by moving forward can you find liberation.

ZH: 越过那条河，你会看到向前的道路。
EN: Cross that river and you will see the way forward.

ZH: 向前冲，即使是缓慢的进步也是进步。
EN: Charge forward, even slow progress is progress.
